        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Nothing will stop you from moving forward. Each time you use an action with the move trait, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to saves against effects that would impose the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Fatigued], @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized], @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Paralyzed], slowed, or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Suppressed] conditions until the end of your next turn. When you would be fatigued, immobilized, paralyzed, slowed, or suppressed for at least 2 rounds, reduce that duration by 1 round.</p>"
        },
        "level": {
            "value": 1
        },
